<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Harry – Frontend Developer CV</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --ink:        #1a1f2e;
      --accent:     #1a56db;   /* trustworthy bright blue */
      --rule:       #1a56db;   /* replaces red lines */
      --muted:      #4b5563;
      --light:      #f3f6ff;
      --page:       #ffffff;
      --border:     #d1daf0;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--light);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.65;
      padding: 32px 16px;
    }

    .page {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: var(--page);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 52px 60px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(26, 86, 219, 0.07);
    }

    /* ── HEADER ── */
    header {
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--rule);
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
      font-size: 42px;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
      color: var(--ink);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    header .role {
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-top: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    header .meta {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px 20px;
    }

    header .meta a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    header .meta a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ── SECTIONS ── */
    section { margin-bottom: 30px; }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 2.5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--rule);
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    /* ── PROFILE ── */
    .profile p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13.5px;
    }

    /* ── SKILLS ── */
    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 100px 1fr;
      row-gap: 6px;
      column-gap: 16px;
      font-size: 13.5px;
    }

    .skill-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .skill-value { color: var(--muted); }

    /* ── PROJECTS ── */
    .project { margin-bottom: 18px; }

    .project-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .project-name {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .project-name .mk {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-right: 4px;
    }

    .project-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .project-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .project-desc {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .project ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    .project ul li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 14px;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .project ul li::before {
      content: '–';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .stack {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    /* ── EDUCATION ── */
    .edu-item { margin-bottom: 14px; }

    .edu-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .edu-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .edu-date {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .edu-item ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .edu-item ul li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 14px;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .edu-item ul li::before {
      content: '–';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ── OFFER ── */
    .offer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .offer-block h4 {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13.5px;
      color: var(--ink);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .offer-block ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .offer-block ul li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding-left: 14px;
      position: relative;
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .offer-block ul li::before {
      content: '–';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      margin-top: 28px;
      padding-top: 16px;
      border-top: 1.5px solid var(--rule);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px 24px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer a {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .page { padding: 32px 24px; }
      .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .skills-grid { grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="page">

    <!-- HEADER -->
    <header>
      <h1>Harry</h1>
      <div class="role">Frontend Developer</div>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>Self-taught · 19 years old · Available for work</span>
        <a href="mailto:honeycodes24@gmail.com">honeycodes24@gmail.com</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24</a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/honey-gupta-5b686b366/" target="_blank">linkedin.com/in/honey-gupta</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- PROFILE -->
    <section class="profile">
      <div class="section-title">Profile</div>
      <p>Self-taught frontend developer with a strong foundation in modern web technologies. I build fast, visually sharp, fully responsive web experiences from scratch — no templates, no shortcuts. At 19, I have already designed and deployed 6 real-world projects including a luxury restaurant website, an e-commerce storefront, a Netflix clone, and an admin dashboard. I combine technical precision with strong design intuition to deliver products that clients are proud to show.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- SKILLS -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-title">Technical Skills</div>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <span class="skill-label">Core</span>
        <span class="skill-value">HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript (ES6+)</span>
        <span class="skill-label">Frameworks</span>
        <span class="skill-value">React.js, Next.js 14, Tailwind CSS</span>
        <span class="skill-label">Animation</span>
        <span class="skill-value">Framer Motion, GSAP, CSS Animations, Parallax</span>
        <span class="skill-label">Tools</span>
        <span class="skill-value">Git, GitHub, VS Code, Figma, Vercel</span>
        <span class="skill-label">Learning</span>
        <span class="skill-value">Node.js, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, REST APIs</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROJECTS -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-title">Projects</div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·I</span> Al Dente Gourmet Restaurant</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/Restarurant-v2" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/Restarurant-v2</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Full luxury restaurant website with cinematic design, parallax scrolling, scroll-triggered animations, and a reservation system.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Built entirely from scratch with no templates or frameworks — pure HTML, CSS, and JavaScript</li>
          <li>Implemented multi-layer parallax effect and GSAP-style scroll animations for premium feel</li>
          <li>Fully responsive across all screen sizes with mobile-first approach</li>
          <li>Deployed on Vercel with custom domain and live reservation form</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Parallax, Vercel</div>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·II</span> Street Style E-Commerce Store</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/StreetStyle-E-Com-Website" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/StreetStyle-E-Com-Website</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Full e-commerce storefront with product catalog, cart functionality, filters, and checkout UI.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Built product listing, cart state management, and filter logic entirely in React</li>
          <li>Implemented responsive grid layout with smooth hover animations on product cards</li>
          <li>Clean component architecture with reusable UI components throughout</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: React, CSS Modules, JavaScript, Vercel</div>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·III</span> QuickBite Food Delivery App</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/Food-delivery" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/Food-delivery</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Modern food delivery landing page with restaurant browsing, menu sections, and order flow UI.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Designed and built a multi-section landing page with animated hero and menu cards</li>
          <li>Used Tailwind CSS utility classes for rapid, consistent styling throughout</li>
          <li>Mobile-first responsive design with smooth scroll and section transitions</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: React, Tailwind CSS, JavaScript, Vercel</div>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·IV</span> Admin Control Panel Dashboard</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/Admin-Dashboard" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/Admin-Dashboard</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Full admin dashboard with analytics charts, data tables, user management, and responsive sidebar.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Integrated Chart.js for live-updating analytics graphs and KPI displays</li>
          <li>Built collapsible sidebar navigation with role-based section visibility</li>
          <li>Responsive layout that adapts cleanly from desktop to tablet screens</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: React, Chart.js, Tailwind CSS, Vercel</div>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·V</span> Netflix UI Clone</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/Netflix-clone" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/Netflix-clone</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Pixel-perfect Netflix interface clone with dynamic content rows, hover previews, and live API data.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Integrated TMDB API for real movie/TV show data across all content rows</li>
          <li>Replicated Netflix's hover expand card animation and thumbnail preview behavior</li>
          <li>Demonstrates precision UI engineering — matching design at component level</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: React, CSS, Vercel</div>
      </div>

      <div class="project">
        <div class="project-header">
          <span class="project-name"><span class="mk">MK·VI</span> Real-Time Weather App</span>
          <a class="project-link" href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24/Weather-Web-App" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24/Weather-Web-App</a>
        </div>
        <p class="project-desc">Real-time weather application with city search, live API data, 5-day forecast, and dynamic UI.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Consumed OpenWeather REST API with async/await and handled loading and error states</li>
          <li>Dynamic background and icon changes based on current weather conditions</li>
          <li>Clean, minimal UI with smooth transitions between city data updates</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="stack">Stack: JavaScript, OpenWeather API, CSS, Vercel</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EDUCATION -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-title">Education</div>

      <div class="edu-item">
        <div class="edu-header">
          <span class="edu-title">Self-Taught Frontend Developer · Independent</span>
          <span class="edu-date">2023 – Present</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Learned HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, and Next.js through documentation, projects, and real-world building</li>
          <li>Completed 6 deployed projects across restaurants, e-commerce, SaaS, and utility apps</li>
          <li>Actively studying system design, backend fundamentals, and TypeScript to expand full-stack capability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="edu-item">
        <div class="edu-header">
          <span class="edu-title">Higher Secondary Education · India</span>
          <span class="edu-date">2023 – 2025</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Completed 12th grade while simultaneously building real web projects</li>
          <li>No formal computer science training — all technical skills are self-acquired</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WHAT I OFFER -->
    <section>
      <div class="section-title">What I Offer</div>
      <div class="offer-grid">
        <div class="offer-block">
          <h4>For Freelance Clients</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Landing pages from ₹8,000 · Business websites from ₹18,000 · Web apps from ₹35,000</li>
            <li>All projects delivered on time, deployed live, and fully responsive across devices</li>
            <li>Direct communication — no agencies, no middlemen, no templates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="offer-block">
          <h4>For Companies &amp; Startups</h4>
          <ul>
            <li>Strong React fundamentals with real project experience — not just tutorial builds</li>
            <li>Eye for design — I build things that look as good as they function</li>
            <li>Fast learner with a bias toward shipping — I figure things out and get things done</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <footer>
      <span>Portfolio: <a href="https://portfolio-steel-tau-35.vercel.app/" target="_blank">portfolio-steel-tau-35.vercel.app</a></span>
      <span>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/HoneyCode24" target="_blank">github.com/HoneyCode24</a></span>
      <span>Email: <a href="mailto:honeycodes24@gmail.com">honeycodes24@gmail.com</a></span>
    </footer>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
